# Keywords
- .gexf: Graph Exchange XML Format (GEXF) is a language for describing complex networks structures, their associated data and dynamics. 
- .tiff: Tag Image File Format(TIFF) is an industry-standard raster graphics file format recognized for its high-quality image storage.
- Gephi Lite: Gephi Lite is a free, web-based, and installation-free version of the popular Gephi desktop software used for visual network and graph analysis. Gephi Lite Link: https://lite.gephi.org

